These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, bus
There 2 different types of food: grapes, mango
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, gardening
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4
4. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | subway     | bus     |
| Food   | mango     | grapes |
| Hobby   | board-games | gardening  |
| Cigar           | game    | prince |
| Flower         | tulip   | bellflower       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, chess
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, pop
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower      | marigold    | aconite |
| Hobby           | chess  | dancing     |
| Birthday   | march       | august      |
| Nationality           | egyptian        | mexican      |
| Music-Genre         | pop | electronic     |

