.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, coral
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, superhero
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, july
2 different pets are kept: bird, goat
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes coral is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Color         | coral     | grey    |
| Movie-Genre           | animation     | superhero |
| Birthday   | july    | august   |
| Pet         | bird | goat   |
| Beverage     | juice | lemonade |

