There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, ivory
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, iris
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, security-guard
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, cooking
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the security-guard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| House          | farmhouse     | colonial     |
| Color   | yellow   | ivory        |
| Flower   | iris      | rose         |
| Job   | security-guard | musician       |
| Hobby         | reading  | cooking |

