2 different games are played: poker, monopoly
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, light-blue
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
2. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport          | lacrosse | ice-hockey |
| Birthday           | september      | december     |
| Game   | monopoly    | poker        |
| Flower   | balloon-flower  | sunflower   |
