House: townhouse, cottage
City: edinburgh, liverpool
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, swimming
1. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the american##1
4. the cottage house is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |
| Nationality      | brazilian    | american         |
| Movie-Genre           | sports | comedy |
| House   | townhouse  | cottage       |
| City           | edinburgh     | liverpool  |
| Sport     | baseball     | swimming         |

